text: Branislav Mojićević (; born 20 August 1986) is a Serbian singer. He rose to fame in 2004, after winning the first season of Zvezde Granda, which earned him a record deal with Grand Production. In addition, Mojićević also won the second season of the Serbian version of Your Face Sounds Familiar in 2014.
